As a JIRA Administrator, I would like to have a centralised page that explains which conditions make a user an active user counting towards to my license in use.

Currently we have some documentations mentioning that if a user is member of jira-user group the user will count in the license usage, and does not mention the Global Permission, and other mentioning the 'Active' checkbox.

It would be better if we had a central documentation, explaining when the user counts towards to the license, and in any other documentation that mention active user create link to the central doc.

